Install OpenBUGS from
http://www.openbugs.net/w/Downloads

Optionally (not required for standard models) install WinBUGS from
http://www.mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk/software/bugs/the-bugs-project-winbugs/

Please use the following command to install the required R-packages:

install.packages(c("Rcpp", "RcppArmadillo",
	           "R2WinBUGS", "ggplot2", "gridExtra", "GenSA", "mvtnorm"),
                 dependencies=TRUE)

Finally install the crmPack from the local zip file:

install.packages("crmPack_0.0-6.zip", rep=NULL)

